title: DOJ's Proposed Jury Questions 'Risks Tainting' Bankman-Fried's Panel, Defense Says
description: Sam Bankman-Fried's attorneys objected to some of the U.S. Department of Justice's proposed voir dire questions in a late Friday filing, saying they may miss potential juror bias or otherwise lead to jurors making assumptions about the case.
